08:25.739 --> 08:27.013
or you can do this.

08:27.608 --> 08:29.476
- Okay.
- You are on your own, buddy.

08:29.576 --> 08:30.748
I'll be in the car.

08:31.879 --> 08:33.756
I'm gonna concede this game.

08:35.515 --> 08:39.123
Dr. Henning to pediatrics.
Dr. Henning to pediatrics, please.

08:41.255 --> 08:43.496
Hi. Thank you.

08:43.823 --> 08:45.993
Give her baby aspirin
until her fever reduces.

08:46.093 --> 08:47.094
Okay.

08:49.062 --> 08:50.700
She don't look too bad.

09:00.641 --> 09:03.588
- I'm trying, Ellie.
- Not hard enough, Dad.

09:25.032 --> 09:26.978
- She still sleeping?
- Yeah.

09:28.068 --> 09:29.069
All the kids are home sick today,

09:29.169 --> 09:31.205
so you're gonna have to stay here
and take care of them.

09:31.305 --> 09:33.182
I have a big history test I can't miss.

09:33.640 --> 09:35.085
Okay, well, I'll...

09:35.576 --> 09:37.055
I'll call Grandma and...

09:48.789 --> 09:50.657
There's a party at Tom's tonight.

09:50.757 --> 09:52.793
- You want to come over?
- No, no, daddy-o.

09:52.893 --> 09:57.398
I'm going to Motorcycle Rita's
to get drunk and have sex and do drugs.

09:57.498 --> 09:59.566
No doll's called Motorcycle Rita.

09:59.666 --> 10:02.569
Yes, there is. And that's where
Marijuana Millie's going tonight.

10:02.669 --> 10:04.004
No doll's named Marijuana.

10:04.104 --> 10:05.572
Okay, maybe not your dolls,

10:05.672 --> 10:08.809
but my dolls do a lot of interesting things
yours would never do.

10:08.909 --> 10:12.356
Well, my dolls like to go camping
all the time at Lake Don Pedro.

10:12.613 --> 10:13.747
And eat tacos and swim.

10:13.847 --> 10:17.192
Who cares about tacos and Lake Don Pedro?

10:18.452 --> 10:20.193
What's been up with you lately?

10:21.121 --> 10:23.257
I thought we were playing dolls
and having fun and stuff like that,

10:23.357 --> 10:25.860
and all of a sudden
your doll is out of control.

10:27.261 --> 10:29.263
- Millie used to own a bakery.
- She sold it.

10:29.363 --> 10:31.001
Can't be naked and own a bakery.

10:31.999 --> 10:33.034
I'm going home.

10:34.868 --> 10:35.969
Wait.

10:36.069 --> 10:37.905
I thought we were gonna make s'mores,

10:38.005 --> 10:41.043
and camp out in the backyard with the
Little Elvis and play records all night long.

10:41.275 --> 10:43.811
It's not gonna be any fun
if it's just me and him.

10:43.911 --> 10:46.213
Aren't we a little old
to be playing with dolls?

10:46.313 --> 10:48.657
Yeah, that'll be the day.

10:50.017 --> 10:51.462
I'll see you later.

11:07.267 --> 11:09.069
Come on. Ellie's all right.

11:09.169 --> 11:10.938
You have no idea how bad it is, Billy.

11:11.038 --> 11:13.607
She's no fun anymore.
She doesn't even want to play dolls.

11:13.707 --> 11:15.108
You guys still play dolls?

11:15.208 --> 11:16.643
Stop giving me the business.

11:16.743 --> 11:20.418
How would an autographed picture
of Mrs. Roosevelt make Ellie be fun again?

11:20.814 --> 11:21.918
It just would.

11:22.749 --> 11:25.686
Billy, I'm 15 years old, okay?

11:25.786 --> 11:29.393
Fifteen is the age when girls start
to lose it and Ellie's almost 16.

11:29.723 --> 11:31.191
- So what do you think that means?
- I really...

11:31.291 --> 11:33.328
- I really have no idea.
- Of course, you're a boy.

11:34.061 --> 11:37.030
Are you going
to the Rock Around the Clock hop?

11:37.130 --> 11:40.134
If no other fellow has asked you to go,
we could go together.

11:41.068 --> 11:43.804
I mean, I'm sure... I'm sure
that you have a lot of guys you like, so.

11:43.904 --> 11:46.817
Listen, Billy,
'cause I'm only gonna say this once.

11:47.107 --> 11:51.283
I know you think us girls think about
you guys all the time, but we don't.

11:51.712 --> 11:52.813
Okay?

11:52.913 --> 11:54.415
So I'll see you soon.

11:54.848 --> 11:57.885
And next time, can I have my cone swirled
instead of just plain vanilla?

11:57.985 --> 11:59.720
And can you dip it, too, please?

11:59.820 --> 12:01.766
- Yeah, sure.
- Au revoir.

12:09.763 --> 12:10.935
"Dear Max,

12:11.865 --> 12:14.004
"thank you so much for your letter.

12:14.901 --> 12:17.507
"At the moment,
I'm out of pictures of myself.

12:18.839 --> 12:20.477
"But I was thinking

12:20.874 --> 12:23.744
"maybe someday you and your friend Ellie

12:23.844 --> 12:26.347
"can come to visit me
at my home in New York.

12:28.181 --> 12:30.252
"Sincerely, Eleanor Roosevelt."

12:43.330 --> 12:45.833
Now you look like you came from New York.

12:50.070 --> 12:52.744
- Don't forget to check the mail, by the way.
- All right.

13:04.418 --> 13:06.520
Guess what? Okay, I wrote
a letter to Eleanor Roosevelt

13:06.620 --> 13:08.722
to get an autographed picture for you
and she wrote me back,

13:08.822 --> 13:12.770
and she wants to meet us, so pack your bags
because we're going to New York!

13:13.627 --> 13:15.038
We're going to New York!

13:16.797 --> 13:17.864
Gee whiz!

13:17.964 --> 13:21.268
...rainfall have left many homes
in the metro area knee deep in floodwater.

13:21.368 --> 13:23.737
Power was out for three hours
in eastern metro

13:23.837 --> 13:27.741
because of downed hydro-fines
and police report at feast 200 accidents.

13:27.841 --> 13:29.843
