15:47.180 --> 15:49.583
and I'll tell my dad I'm staying with you
over the weekend,

15:49.683 --> 15:52.552
and you tell your mom
you're staying with me over the weekend,

15:52.652 --> 15:55.895
and then when they find out,
we'll already be long gone.

15:56.056 --> 15:57.157
You two don't have no money.

15:57.257 --> 15:59.059
Shut your mouth, Billy.
I know where we can get some.

15:59.159 --> 16:03.237
