not to tell a soul, not even Dad.

16:34.294 --> 16:36.263
Dad don't want me
keeping secrets from him!

16:36.363 --> 16:37.933
I'm doing something for Mom.

16:38.198 --> 16:39.233
But to do it,

16:40.133 --> 16:41.601
I have to sell her piano.

16:41.701 --> 16:44.237
And if she were here right now,
she'd be okay with it

16:44.337 --> 16:46.908
because people are more important
than stuff, right?

16:50.577 --> 16:51.988
I'll give you 5 bucks.

17:47.067 --> 17:49.809
My mom and Marilyn Monroe
died on the same day.

17:51.071 --> 17:55.076
I imagined Marilyn picking my mom up
like some kind of girls' night out.

17:56.309 --> 17:57.444
Just the two of them.

17:57.544 --> 18:01.890
The 1948 Chrysler Windsor
with a drop top in Robin's egg blue?

18:02.148 --> 18:04.424
- The very one.
- Smile!

18:05.218 --> 18:06.319
We're going to New York!

18:06.419 --> 18:09.366
They'd hop into Marilyn's pink Thunderbird
and hit the road.

18:10.256 --> 18:12.031
Didn't seem so lonely.

18:12.692 --> 18:13.727
Seemed nice.

18:23.269 --> 18:28.446
V-A-C-A-T-I-O-N, in the summer sun!

18:28.675 --> 18:31.451
Put away the books, we're out of school

18:31.811 --> 18:34.614
The weather's warm but we play it cool

18:34.714 --> 18:38.924
We're on vacation in the summer sun!

18:39.352 --> 18:41.958
How many miles to New York?

18:42.155 --> 18:43.323
3,000

18:43.423 --> 18:44.791
- You kidding me?
- No.

18:44.891 --> 18:48.328
And here is our money.

18:48.428 --> 18:50.530
That's all we've got
so put it in a safe spot, okay?

18:50.630 --> 18:53.033
Holy moly, that's a lot of moolah.

18:53.133 --> 18:55.477
I don't think I've ever seen
this much money in my whole life.

18:57.637 --> 18:59.378
- All safe.
- Great.

19:00.173 --> 19:02.153
Okay, I was gonna wait,

19:02.509 --> 19:06.457
but since we're about to have
the time of our lives...

19:07.747 --> 19:09.516
Okay, just some pictures of Mrs. Roosevelt

19:09.616 --> 19:12.285
that I cut out of the library books
during study hall.

19:12.385 --> 19:14.254
And I thought that we could put
some of our own pictures

19:14.354 --> 19:17.198
- and some stuff in the back, too.
